headline: RTX's Collins Aerospace to provide U.S. Army Black Hawk helicopters with modular, third party-capable avionics
summary: Collins Aerospace, an RTX (NYSE: RTX) business, has received an $80 million contract to upgrade the avionics system of U.S. Army Black Hawk helicopters for the H-60M MOSA Avionics Architecture Solution program.
